# Enhanced PDP Naming Conventions

Observed patterns from `page-mens-hrt-enhanced-pdp-1.php`. Use this as the authoritative reference for class naming — it reflects what's actually in production templates.

> **Note:** `SECTION_LIBRARY.md` uses BEM-style naming (`hero__title`, `hero__content`) as an abstraction layer. Actual templates use **flat compound naming** instead. Follow the flat style documented here.

---

## Section Class Naming

Sections use a **primary descriptive name** plus optional **modifier utility classes**:

```php
<section class="[primary-name] [modifier-classes]" [id="anchor"]>
```

### Examples from this template

| Primary Name | Modifier Classes | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `boost-your-testosterone hero` | `border-bottom` | Two semantic names on one section |
| `marquee trustpilot-ratings` | `border-bottom extended-center-border-below` | |
| `how-it-works social-videos` | `extended-center-border-below` | |
| `benefits-timeline` | `border-bottom extended-center-border-above` | |
| `proven-benefits` | `border-bottom extended-center-border-above` | |
| `injections-section` | `border-bottom extended-center-border-below` | Has `id="injections-section"` for anchor |
| `testimonials` | `extended-center-border-below` | |
| `alternatives` | `extended-center-border-above` | |

### Section Border Modifier Classes

These control the decorative center-line border between sections:

| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `border-bottom` | Adds a bottom border to the section |
| `extended-center-border-below` | Extends a vertical center border downward into the next section |
| `extended-center-border-above` | Extends a vertical center border upward into the previous section |

These can be combined. Typical pairings:
- `border-bottom extended-center-border-below` — section ends with border that continues down
- `border-bottom extended-center-border-above` — section receives border from above

