## Responsive Visibility Classes

```php
class="desktop-only"            // Hidden on tablet and smaller
class="tablet-and-smaller-only" // Hidden on desktop
```

Used in `injections-section` to swap between a static desktop grid and a mobile carousel for the same image set.

