## FAQ Icon Pattern (Actual)

The actual template uses **two `<span>` elements** for the +/× animation, NOT a plain `+` text character:

```php
<span class="faq-icon">
    <span class="icon-line line-horizontal"></span>
    <span class="icon-line line-vertical"></span>
</span>
```

The `.line-vertical` is rotated/hidden via CSS on expand.

