## `render_cta_block()` Signature

```php
render_cta_block($url, $label, $secondary = false, $extra_class = '');

// Scroll to anchor on same page:
render_cta_block('#injections-section', 'Test my T-Levels');

// Checkout URL, default primary style:
render_cta_block($checkout_url, 'Test My T-Levels');

// With custom class on the wrapper:
render_cta_block($checkout_url, 'Test My T-Levels', false, 'proven-benefits-cta-block');
```

