## Script Enqueuing with JS Data

When a template needs to pass PHP data to JavaScript (e.g., `themeFolder`), use `add_action` + `wp_localize_script` instead of a direct enqueue call:

```php
add_action('wp_enqueue_scripts', function() use ($template_name, $theme_folder) {
    wp_enqueue_script('hone-page-' . $template_name);
    wp_localize_script('hone-page-' . $template_name, 'honePageData', array(
        'themeFolder' => $theme_folder
    ));
});
```

In JS, access via `window.honePageData.themeFolder`.

