## `$additional_disclaimers` Global

For page-specific legal disclaimers appended in the footer:

```php
global $class_names, $additional_disclaimers;

$additional_disclaimers = [
    'Results may vary. Medications are prescribed if deemed to be clinically necessary...'
];
```

